MailCongress Charter

Iteration 1 - October 2, 2010

  1. Vision
    People are increasingly becoming reliant upon electronic means of getting in contact with their political representatives.
    The irony is that communication channels like email are pretty much ignored. MailCongress wants to provide an interface
    to send physical mail to the selected politicians.

